        <li class="default">right</li>
      </ol>
    </dd>
    <dt>width <code>string</code></dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Acceptable values: any valid CSS width (px, rem, etc)</p>
      <p><em>Notice: by default the dropdown list has a
          <code class="dummy-code">min-width</code>
